    },
    {
      "id": "5TEuZqA3LevHALK4EbNBr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 234,
      "y": 238.5,
      "width": 574.2395629882812,
      "height": 1225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bdL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 479309004,
      "version": 818,
      "versionNonce": 413832948,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783241991983,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions?\n\nq. like fb messenger app?\nyes\n\nq. friends change location? how frequently?\nyes, every few seconds\n\nq. imp features?\nUsers should be able to see from frinds list nearby friends\nlocation gets updted every few seconds\nnotification when friend is nearby\ninactve when friend disappers\n\nq. define nearby?\nin X kms\n\nq. gets notification if nearby\nyes\n\nq. scale?\n1 b users\n10% DAU\n\nq. no of friends ?\n500 friends\n\nFunctioanal req:\nUsers should be able to see from frinds list nearby friends\nlocation gets updted every few seconds\nnotification when friend is nearby\ninactive when friend disappers\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.9 to 99.99\nScalability\nlow latency\n\nBack of the envelope cal:\n100 m users\n100m * 10 reads per day\n10^9 / 10^5 = 10000 rps\n\nwrites every 30 secs\n100m / 24 * 60 *2 \n= 100 * 10^6 / 48 * 60\n=  100 * 10^6 / 3000\n= 3.3 * 10^4\n= 33000",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions?\n\nq. like fb messenger app?\nyes\n\nq. friends change location? how frequently?\nyes, every few seconds\n\nq. imp features?\nUsers should be able to see from frinds list nearby friends\nlocation gets updted every few seconds\nnotification when friend is nearby\ninactve when friend disappers\n\nq. define nearby?\nin X kms\n\nq. gets notification if nearby\nyes\n\nq. scale?\n1 b users\n10% DAU\n\nq. no of friends ?\n500 friends\n\nFunctioanal req:\nUsers should be able to see from frinds list nearby friends\nlocation gets updted every few seconds\nnotification when friend is nearby\ninactive when friend disappers\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.9 to 99.99\nScalability\nlow latency\n\nBack of the envelope cal:\n100 m users\n100m * 10 reads per day\n10^9 / 10^5 = 10000 rps\n\nwrites every 30 secs\n100m / 24 * 60 *2 \n= 100 * 10^6 / 48 * 60\n=  100 * 10^6 / 3000\n= 3.3 * 10^4\n= 33000",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
